        <item>
            <title>Version 1.0.22</title>
            <sparkle:version>22</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.0.22</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 05:21:52 +0000</pubDate>
            <enclosure
                url="https://github.com/Jootsing-Research/tapkit-releases/releases/download/v1.0.22/TapKit-1.0.22.dmg"
                sparkle:edSignature="V1SX9RYNeeVjcmcJ7Y1LmO1wuRfuKaX/CbUN+BfOPzNBZphDXb3EV3uTghPPpAHolgkLozdQ4VL2DslwlEzDBQ=="
                length="78760781"
                type="application/octet-stream" />
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New</h2>
                <ul><li>Introduced Scan as a first-class segment type with timing validation and stop-and-retry recovery</li><li>Single-key bursts for non-select steps — retry only resends the key that didn't land</li><li>Scan timing validation checks inter-select gaps with per-step recovery (5 next + select + stop)</li><li>Sleep steps now break select grouping so scans only contain the scanning phase</li><li>Consolidated CheckpointReducer, SwitchControlRecoveryReducer, and SegmentedExecutionReducer into one unified SegmentedOperationReducer</li><li>Reject concurrent operations while one is already in progress</li></ul>
            ]]></description>
        </item>

